---
import BaseLayout from "~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <article class="prose mx-auto">
    <header class="not-prose mb-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-zinc-500">Last updated: August 15, 2025</p>
    </header>

    <p>Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your choices.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Usage data (pages visited, interactions)</li>
      <li>Technical data (browser, device, IP)</li>
      <li>Content you submit voluntarily (e.g., newsletter signup)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To operate and improve the site</li>
      <li>To communicate updates with your consent</li>
      <li>To ensure security and prevent abuse</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use cookies and similar technologies for essential functionality, analytics, and preferences. See our <a href="/cookies">Cookie Policy</a> for details.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, correct, or delete your data. Contact us to exercise these rights.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? Contact the site owner listed in our site imprint or <a href="/">home page</a>.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
